substep.ask:
Present the user with:
I understand the request as: {{session.request_restatement}}
Candidate primary tag: {{session.candidate_tag}} Proposed slug: {{session.slug}}
Does this match your intent?
Options: - Confirm: scope is correct, proceed to scaffold and grill - Redirect: scope is wrong; describe how - Adjust tag: scope is right but the candidate tag is wrong; specify the correct tag - Adjust slug: scope and tag are right but the slug should change; specify the new slug - Cancel: stop the workflow

substep.template-output:
Scope locked for this ticket-writing session:

- Restatement: {{session.request_restatement}}
- Primary tag: {{session.candidate_tag}}
- Slug: {{session.slug}}
- Bundle directory (planned): {{session.shared_folder}}/tickets/{{session.slug}}/
- Owner: {{session.owner}}

Next: scaffold the bundle on disk.
